-- Saudi Rabigh Refining Reports Second-Quarter Profit After Loss Year Ago
-- Shaji Mathew
-- 2010-07-20T13:33:46Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-20/saudi-rabigh-refining-reports-second-quarter-profit-after-loss-year-ago.html

          
          
             Rabigh Refining and Petrochemicals
Co., a joint venture between state-owned Saudi Aramco and
Sumitomo Chemical Co. of Japan, reported a second-quarter profit
of 121.8 million riyals after a loss of 236 million riyals in
the year-earlier period. The company made the announcement in a
statement to the Saudi bourse today.  
          
          


  


        